column8: You are but motes of dust...
I shall bring you with me.
This reminds me of when we were children, and we would spar...
Leave me out of it next time.
Don't make me do this, Sett.
Just won't stay dead will it.
You will not touch him, Bull-man.
...I have to help Sett, my lord!
Can't get enough of me, can you?
There's only one of me, Sett.
Why ask for help from him?
I told you to get out!
Get out while you still can.
Looks like I got here just in time.
I thought I'd find you here.
It's been a little while, hasn't it?
I happened to be in the area.
You brazen wretches ought to have turned back.
Come, wretches, and be returned to dust!
The moon shall purge your sins.
All in Elysium should know of us by now.
Let's see how quickly we can wrap this up.
I doubt this will take very long at all.
I shall offer you all eternal slumber...
Let me take care of this.
Don't waste this chance you have!
Give me some room to work.
You're clear of them for now.
We'll leave no trace of this.
And that's the end of that.
...We make a good team, don't we.
Maybe I had a little fun...
That takes care of that, I guess. See you.
You earned this fair and square.
You got a lot of them.
I'll take more down next time.
Should have stayed at your post.
Here, since you did all the work.
Guess you had this well in hand.
How did you get so fast?
I will not let you harm him, Karthus.
They're coming, Sett. Be on your guard.
Think you can beat me again, Sett?
Hm, scared I'll beat you again?
You can be so reckless, Sett...
Neither you nor these wretches ever seem to learn.
I have more work to do...
